<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no, maximum-scale=1.0, viewport-fit=cover">
  <meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-capable" content="yes">
  <meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-status-bar-style" content="black-translucent">
  <meta name="theme-color" content="#0a0a1a">
  <meta name="description" content="Block Smash Puzzle — the addictive block puzzle game! Place blocks, clear lines, score big. Free to play.">
  <meta name="keywords" content="block puzzle, puzzle game, block smash, brain game, casual game">
  <meta property="og:title" content="Block Smash Puzzle">
  <meta property="og:description" content="Place blocks, clear lines, score big! The most addictive puzzle game.">
  <meta property="og:type" content="website">
  <title>Block Smash Puzzle</title>
  <link rel="manifest" href="/manifest.json">
  <link rel="apple-touch-icon" href="/icons/icon-192.png">
  <style>
    :root {
      --safe-top: env(safe-area-inset-top, 0px);
      --safe-bottom: env(safe-area-inset-bottom, 0px);
      --safe-left: env(safe-area-inset-left, 0px);
      --safe-right: env(safe-area-inset-right, 0px);
      --board-size: min(calc(100vw - 32px), min(calc(100dvh - 310px), 440px));
      --cell-gap: 2px;
      --cell-size: calc((var(--board-size) - 16px - var(--cell-gap) * 7) / 8);
      --piece-cell: clamp(16px, 4.5vw, 26px);
      --ui-radius: 14px;
      --bg-primary: #0a0a1a;
      --bg-card: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
      --border-subtle: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
      --text-dim: rgba(255,255,255,0.35);
      --accent-blue: #4d96ff;
      --accent-purple: #a855f7;
      --accent-gold: #ffd93d;
      --accent-green: #6bcb77;
      --accent-red: #ff6b6b;
    }
    @media (min-width: 600px) {
      :root {
        --board-size: min(calc(100vw - 80px), min(calc(100dvh - 340px), 520px));
        --piece-cell: clamp(20px, 3.5vw, 32px);
        --cell-gap: 3px;
      }
    }
    @media (min-width: 1024px) {
      :root {
        --board-size: min(480px, calc(100dvh - 360px));
        --piece-cell: 28px;
        --cell-gap: 3px;
      }
    }
    @media (max-height: 500px) and (orientation: landscape) {
      :root {
        --board-size: min(calc(100dvh - 100px), calc(100vw * 0.45));
        --piece-cell: clamp(12px, 3vw, 20px);
      }
    }
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', system-ui, sans-serif;
      background: var(--bg-primary);
      color: #fff;
      overflow: hidden;
      height: 100vh; height: 100dvh;
      width: 100vw;
      touch-action: none;
      user-select: none;
      -webkit-user-select: none;
      -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
    }
    #bg-canvas {
      position: fixed; inset: 0; z-index: 0;
      pointer-events: none; opacity: 0.5;
    }
    #fx-canvas {
      position: fixed; inset: 0; z-index: 50;
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    /* === SPLASH === */
    #splash {
      position: fixed; inset: 0; z-index: 9999;
      background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 30%, #1a1a4e 0%, #0a0a1a 70%);
      display: flex; flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      transition: opacity 0.7s cubic-bezier(.4,0,.2,1), transform 0.7s cubic-bezier(.4,0,.2,1);
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    #splash.hide { opacity: 0; transform: scale(1.05); pointer-events: none; }
    .splash-blocks { position: absolute; inset: 0; overflow: hidden; pointer-events: none; }
    .splash-block {
      position: absolute; border-radius: 8px; opacity: 0;
      animation: floatBlock 5s ease-in-out infinite;
    }
    @keyframes floatBlock {
      0% { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(100vh) rotate(0deg) scale(0.5); }
      15% { opacity: 0.4; } 85% { opacity: 0.25; }
      100% { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(-20vh) rotate(360deg) scale(1.2); }
    }
    .splash-logo-container {
      position: relative; z-index: 2; text-align: center;
      animation: logoEntry 1s cubic-bezier(0.34, 1.56, 0.64, 1) forwards; opacity: 0;
    }
    @keyframes logoEntry {
      0% { opacity: 0; transform: scale(0.3) translateY(40px); }
      100% { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1) translateY(0); }
    }
    .splash-icon {
      font-size: 5em; margin-bottom: 10px;
      animation: iconBounce 3s ease-in-out infinite;
      filter: drop-shadow(0 0 40px rgba(77,150,255,0.5));
    }
    @keyframes iconBounce {
      0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0) rotate(0deg); }
      25% { transform: translateY(-12px) rotate(-5deg); }
      75% { transform: translateY(-6px) rotate(5deg); }
    }
    .splash-title {
      font-size: clamp(2.2em, 8vw, 3.5em); font-weight: 900; letter-spacing: 4px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff6b6b 0%, #ffd93d 25%, #6bcb77 50%, #4d96ff 75%, #a855f7 100%);
      background-size: 300% 300%;
      -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; background-clip: text;
      animation: gradientShift 3s ease-in-out infinite;
      filter: drop-shadow(0 3px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.5));
    }
    @keyframes gradientShift { 0%, 100% { background-position: 0% 50%; } 50% { background-position: 100% 50%; } }
    .splash-subtitle {
      font-size: clamp(0.7em, 3vw, 1em); opacity: 0.4; margin-top: 4px;
      letter-spacing: 8px; text-transform: uppercase; font-weight: 800;
    }
    .splash-loader {
      position: relative; z-index: 2;
      width: min(240px, 60vw); height: 5px; margin-top: 40px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06); border-radius: 3px; overflow: hidden;
      animation: fadeInUp 0.6s 0.3s both;
    }
    @keyframes fadeInUp { from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(15px); } to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); } }
    .splash-loader-fill {
      height: 100%; border-radius: 3px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--accent-blue), var(--accent-purple), var(--accent-red), var(--accent-gold));
      background-size: 300% 100%;
      animation: loaderFill 2s ease-out forwards, loaderShimmer 1.5s linear infinite;
      width: 0%;
    }
    @keyframes loaderFill { 0% { width: 0%; } 20% { width: 35%; } 50% { width: 70%; } 80% { width: 90%; } 100% { width: 100%; } }
    @keyframes loaderShimmer { 0% { background-position: 0% 50%; } 100% { background-position: 300% 50%; } }
    .splash-tap {
      position: relative; z-index: 2; margin-top: 36px; font-size: 1.1em; font-weight: 800;
      opacity: 0; letter-spacing: 3px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85);
      animation: tapAppear 0.5s 2s forwards; cursor: pointer;
    }
    .splash-tap.ready { animation: tapAppear 0.5s forwards, tapPulse 2s 0.5s ease-in-out infinite; }
    @keyframes tapAppear { from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(10px); } to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); } }
    @keyframes tapPulse { 0%, 100% { opacity: 0.7; transform: scale(1); } 50% { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1.05); } }
    .splash-version {
      position: absolute; bottom: calc(20px + var(--safe-bottom)); z-index: 2;
      font-size: 0.55em; opacity: 0.12; letter-spacing: 4px; font-weight: 600;
    }

    /* === GAME CONTAINER === */
    #game-container {
      display: none; flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center; justify-content: flex-start;
      height: 100vh; height: 100dvh;
      padding: calc(6px + var(--safe-top)) 14px calc(6px + var(--safe-bottom));
      max-width: 560px; margin: 0 auto;
      overflow: hidden; position: relative; z-index: 1;
      animation: gameContainerIn 0.6s ease-out;
    }
    #game-container.show { display: flex; }
    @keyframes gameContainerIn { from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(12px); } to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); } }
    @media (max-height: 500px) and (orientation: landscape) {
      #game-container {
        flex-direction: row; flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: center; align-items: flex-start;
        max-width: 100%; padding: 4px 12px; gap: 8px;
      }
      .header { width: 100%; }
      #board-container { order: 1; }
      #pieces-container { order: 2; flex-direction: column; max-height: calc(100dvh - 60px); min-height: unset; max-width: 180px; gap: 4px; }
      .piece-slot { min-height: 50px; }
      #level-bar-container, .daily-challenge { display: none; }
    }

    /* === HEADER === */
    .header {
      display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
      width: 100%; padding: 2px 0 4px; flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    .game-title {
      font-size: clamp(0.9em, 4vw, 1.2em); font-weight: 900; letter-spacing: 1.5px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff6b6b, #ffd93d, #6bcb77, #4d96ff);
      background-size: 200% 200%;
      -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; background-clip: text;
      animation: gradientShift 4s ease-in-out infinite;
    }
    .header-right { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; }
    .score-section { display: flex; gap: 6px; }
    .score-box {
      text-align: center; background: var(--bg-card);
      border-radius: 12px; padding: 4px 14px; min-width: 68px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle); backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
    }
    .score-box .label { font-size: 0.45em; opacity: 0.35; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 2.5px; font-weight: 700; }
    .score-box .value { font-size: 1.3em; font-weight: 900; font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums; }
    .score-box:last-child .value { color: var(--accent-gold); }
    .new-best { color: var(--accent-gold) !important; animation: pulse 0.5s ease-in-out; }
    @keyframes pulse { 50% { transform: scale(1.3); } }
    .gear-btn {
      background: var(--bg-card); border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
      border-radius: 10px; cursor: pointer; padding: 5px 8px;
      opacity: 0.5; transition: all 0.2s; font-size: 0.95em; color: #fff;
    }
    .gear-btn:active { opacity: 1; transform: scale(0.92); }

    /* === LEVEL BAR === */
    #level-bar-container { width: 100%; padding: 1px 0; flex-shrink: 0; }
    .level-info { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; margin-bottom: 2px; }
    #level-badge {
      font-size: 0.62em; font-weight: 800; color: var(--accent-gold);
      background: rgba(255,215,0,0.06); padding: 2px 8px; border-radius: 6px; border: 1px solid rgba(255,215,0,0.1);
    }
    .level-title-text { font-size: 0.52em; opacity: 0.3; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1.5px; }
    .streak-badge { font-size: 0.58em; font-weight: 700; color: var(--accent-red); margin-left: auto; }
    .xp-bar-bg { width: 100%; height: 3px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04); border-radius: 2px; overflow: hidden; }
    .xp-bar-fill {
      height: 100%; background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--accent-blue), var(--accent-purple));
      border-radius: 2px; transition: width 0.6s ease-out; box-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(77,150,255,0.3);
    }
    .xp-label { font-size: 0.45em; opacity: 0.18; text-align: right; margin-top: 1px; }

    /* === DAILY CHALLENGE === */
    .daily-challenge {
      width: 100%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255,107,107,0.04), rgba(77,150,255,0.04));
      border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle); border-radius: 10px; padding: 4px 12px; margin-bottom: 2px; flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    .daily-challenge.completed {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(107,203,119,0.08), rgba(107,203,119,0.02));
      border-color: rgba(107,203,119,0.15);
    }
    .daily-left { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; }
    .daily-icon { font-size: 1em; }
    .daily-name { font-size: 0.58em; font-weight: 700; }
    .daily-desc { font-size: 0.45em; opacity: 0.3; }
    .daily-progress-ring { font-size: 0.58em; font-weight: 800; color: var(--accent-gold); min-width: 32px; text-align: center; }

    /* === BOARD === */
    #board-container { position: relative; margin: 3px 0; flex-shrink: 0; }
    #board-container.shake { animation: boardShake 0.35s ease-out; }
    @keyframes boardShake {
      0% { transform: translate(0, 0); } 15% { transform: translate(-3px, 2px); }
      30% { transform: translate(3px, -2px); } 45% { transform: translate(-2px, 1px); }
      60% { transform: translate(2px, -1px); } 75% { transform: translate(-1px, 1px); }
      100% { transform: translate(0, 0); }
    }
    .board-toolbar { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; width: 100%; margin-bottom: 3px; }
    #board {
      display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(8, var(--cell-size));
      gap: var(--cell-gap);
      background: rgba(12, 12, 35, 0.9);
      border-radius: 16px; padding: 8px;
      border: 1.5px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
      box-shadow: 0 12px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.5), inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
      position: relative;
    }
    #board::before {
      content: ''; position: absolute; inset: 8px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.012) 1px, transparent 1px),
                  linear-gradient(0deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.012) 1px, transparent 1px);
      background-size: calc(100% / 8) calc(100% / 8);
      pointer-events: none; border-radius: 8px; z-index: 0;
    }
    .cell {
      width: var(--cell-size); height: var(--cell-size);
      border-radius: 6px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.018);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.025);
      transition: all 0.12s ease-out;
      will-change: background, transform, opacity;
      position: relative; z-index: 1;
    }
    body.dragging .cell { transition: none !important; }
    .cell.filled {
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
      border-radius: 6px; position: relative; box-shadow: none;
    }
    .cell.filled::before {
      content: ''; position: absolute; inset: 1px 1px auto 1px; height: 40%;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.28) 0%, rgba(255,255,255,0) 100%);
      border-radius: 5px 5px 50% 50%; pointer-events: none;
    }
    .cell.filled::after {
      content: ''; position: absolute; inset: auto 2px 1px 2px; height: 30%;
      background: linear-gradient(0deg, rgba(0,0,0,0.18) 0%, rgba(0,0,0,0) 100%);
      border-radius: 0 0 4px 4px; pointer-events: none;
    }
    .cell.preview {
      border: 1.5px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.45) !important;
      transform: scale(0.92);
      box-shadow: 0 0 12px rgba(255,255,255,0.15), inset 0 0 8px rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
      border-radius: 6px; z-index: 2;
    }
    .cell.invalid-preview { background: rgba(255,60,60,0.12) !important; border: 1.5px dashed rgba(255,60,60,0.3) !important; }
    .cell.clearing { animation: clearPop 0.45s cubic-bezier(.4,0,.2,1) forwards; }
    @keyframes clearPop {
      0% { transform: scale(1) rotate(0deg); opacity: 1; }
      30% { transform: scale(1.15) rotate(2deg); opacity: 0.9; }
      100% { transform: scale(0) rotate(8deg); opacity: 0; background: transparent; border-color: transparent; }
    }
    .cell.row-hint, .cell.col-hint { box-shadow: inset 0 0 8px rgba(255,215,0,0.15); border-color: rgba(255,215,0,0.12); }
    #board.combo-glow {
      box-shadow: 0 12px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.5), inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,0.04),
                  0 0 30px rgba(255,215,0,0.12), 0 0 60px rgba(255,107,107,0.08);
      transition: box-shadow 0.3s ease-out;
    }
    .cell.just-placed { animation: blockLand 0.25s cubic-bezier(.4,0,.2,1); }
    @keyframes blockLand { 0% { transform: scale(0.6); opacity: 0.5; } 60% { transform: scale(1.08); } 100% { transform: scale(1); opacity: 1; } }

    /* === PIECES TRAY === */
    #pieces-container {
      display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center;
      width: 100%; padding: 6px 2px; gap: 8px;
      flex-shrink: 0; flex-grow: 1;
      max-height: 160px; min-height: 90px;
    }
    .piece-slot {
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      flex: 1; padding: 10px 6px;
      background: var(--bg-card); border-radius: var(--ui-radius); cursor: grab;
      min-height: 85px; max-width: 140px;
      transition: transform 0.25s cubic-bezier(.4,0,.2,1), background 0.2s, opacity 0.3s, box-shadow 0.2s;
      border: 1.5px solid var(--border-subtle); position: relative; overflow: hidden;
    }
    .piece-slot::before {
      content: ''; position: absolute; inset: 0;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.03) 0%, transparent 50%, rgba(255,255,255,0.02) 100%);
      pointer-events: none;
    }
    .piece-slot:active { cursor: grabbing; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06); transform: scale(0.95); }
    .piece-slot.dragging { opacity: 0.12; transform: scale(0.8); }
    .piece-slot.cannot-fit { opacity: 0.15; filter: grayscale(0.8) brightness(0.5); }
    .piece-grid { display: grid; gap: 3px; pointer-events: none; }
    .piece-cell { width: var(--piece-cell); height: var(--piece-cell); border-radius: 5px; pointer-events: none; position: relative; }
    .piece-cell.active { border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12); }
    .piece-cell.active::before {
      content: ''; position: absolute; inset: 1px 1px auto 1px; height: 40%;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.22) 0%, rgba(255,255,255,0) 100%);
      border-radius: 4px 4px 50% 50%; pointer-events: none;
    }
    .piece-cell.empty { background: transparent; }

    /* === DRAG GHOST === */
    #drag-ghost {
      position: fixed; pointer-events: none; z-index: 1000; display: none;
      opacity: 0.92; filter: drop-shadow(0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.7));
      will-change: transform; left: 0; top: 0;
    }
    #drag-ghost .piece-grid { gap: 2px; }
    #drag-ghost .piece-cell { width: var(--cell-size); height: var(--cell-size); border-radius: 6px; }
    #drag-ghost .piece-cell.active { border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15); }
    #drag-ghost .piece-cell.active::before {
      content: ''; position: absolute; inset: 1px 1px auto 1px; height: 40%;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.25) 0%, rgba(255,255,255,0) 100%);
      border-radius: 5px 5px 50% 50%; pointer-events: none;
    }

    /* === POPUPS === */
    .combo-popup {
      position: absolute; top: 50%; left: 50%;
      transform: translate(-50%, -50%); font-size: clamp(1.8em, 6vw, 2.8em); font-weight: 900;
      pointer-events: none; z-index: 100;
      animation: comboFloat 1.2s cubic-bezier(.4,0,.2,1) forwards;
      text-shadow: 0 0 40px currentColor, 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.5); letter-spacing: 2px;
    }
    @keyframes comboFloat {
      0% { opacity: 1; transform: translate(-50%, -50%) scale(0.3) rotate(-5deg); }
      20% { opacity: 1; transform: translate(-50%, -65%) scale(1.3) rotate(2deg); }
      100% { opacity: 0; transform: translate(-50%, -130%) scale(0.7) rotate(0deg); }
    }
    .score-float {
      position: absolute; font-size: 1.3em; font-weight: 900;
      color: var(--accent-gold); pointer-events: none; z-index: 100;
      animation: scoreUp 0.8s ease-out forwards;
      text-shadow: 0 0 12px rgba(255,215,0,0.4), 0 1px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
    }
    @keyframes scoreUp { 0% { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0) scale(1.1); } 100% { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(-45px) scale(0.7); } }
    .perfect-popup {
      position: absolute; top: 50%; left: 50%;
      transform: translate(-50%, -50%); font-size: clamp(1.5em, 5vw, 2.2em); font-weight: 900;
      pointer-events: none; z-index: 110; color: var(--accent-gold);
      animation: perfectFloat 1.8s cubic-bezier(.4,0,.2,1) forwards;
      text-shadow: 0 0 50px rgba(255,215,0,0.6), 0 0 100px rgba(255,215,0,0.3); letter-spacing: 4px;
    }
    @keyframes perfectFloat {
      0% { opacity: 0; transform: translate(-50%, -50%) scale(0.2); }
      20% { opacity: 1; transform: translate(-50%, -55%) scale(1.2); }
      60% { opacity: 1; transform: translate(-50%, -60%) scale(1); }
      100% { opacity: 0; transform: translate(-50%, -80%) scale(0.8); }
    }

    /* === GAME OVER === */
    #game-over {
      display: none; position: fixed; inset: 0;
      background: rgba(5,5,15,0.94); z-index: 200;
      flex-direction: column; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      gap: 14px; backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
      padding: var(--safe-top) 24px var(--safe-bottom);
    }
    #game-over.show { display: flex; animation: gameOverIn 0.5s ease-out; }
    @keyframes gameOverIn { from { opacity: 0; } to { opacity: 1; } }
    #game-over h2 {
      font-size: clamp(2em, 7vw, 2.8em); font-weight: 900; letter-spacing: 4px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent-red), var(--accent-gold));
      -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; background-clip: text;
      filter: drop-shadow(0 2px 10px rgba(255,107,107,0.3));
    }
    #game-over .final-score { font-size: clamp(2.5em, 10vw, 4em); font-weight: 900; text-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(255,255,255,0.1); }
    #game-over .best-label { font-size: 0.75em; opacity: 0.3; letter-spacing: 3px; text-transform: uppercase; }
    #game-over .best-score { font-size: 1.4em; font-weight: 800; color: var(--accent-gold); }
    #game-over .new-record {
      font-size: 1.1em; color: var(--accent-green); font-weight: 800;
      animation: pulse 0.6s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
      text-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(107,203,119,0.4);
    }
    .btn-row { display: flex; gap: 12px; flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: center; }
    .btn {
      padding: 14px 34px; font-size: 1.05em; font-weight: 800;
      border: none; border-radius: 50px; cursor: pointer;
      transition: transform 0.15s, box-shadow 0.15s; color: #fff;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: inherit;
    }
    .btn:active { transform: scale(0.93); }
    .btn-primary {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent-green), var(--accent-blue));
      box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(75,150,255,0.3), inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
    }
    .btn-share {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent-red), var(--accent-gold));
      box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(255,107,107,0.25), inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
    }
    .btn-secondary { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08); }
    .btn-exit {
      background: rgba(255,60,60,0.1); border: 1px solid rgba(255,60,60,0.15);
      color: var(--accent-red); font-size: 0.9em; padding: 10px 28px;
    }
    .btn-exit:active { background: rgba(255,60,60,0.2); }

    .ad-banner-slot {
      width: 100%; max-width: 320px; height: 50px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.01); border-radius: 8px;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      font-size: 0.65em; opacity: 0.08; flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    .action-btn {
      background: var(--bg-card); border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
      color: #fff; font-size: 0.58em; font-weight: 700; padding: 4px 10px;
      border-radius: 8px; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.2s; font-family: inherit;
    }
    .action-btn:active { transform: scale(0.93); background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08); }

    /* === MODALS === */
    #settings-modal {
      display: none; position: fixed; inset: 0;
      background: rgba(5,5,15,0.92); z-index: 300;
      flex-direction: column; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      gap: 16px; backdrop-filter: blur(18px);
    }
    #settings-modal.show { display: flex; animation: fadeIn 0.3s ease-out; }
    @keyframes fadeIn { from { opacity: 0; } to { opacity: 1; } }
    .settings-panel {
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.06) 0%, rgba(255,255,255,0.02) 100%);
      border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
      border-radius: 22px; padding: 26px; width: 88%; max-width: 360px;
    }
    .settings-panel h3 { margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 1.3em; font-weight: 800; }
    .setting-row {
      display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
      padding: 14px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.03); font-size: 0.95em;
    }
    .setting-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
    .toggle {
      width: 50px; height: 28px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      border-radius: 14px; cursor: pointer; position: relative; transition: background 0.25s;
    }
    .toggle.on { background: var(--accent-blue); }
    .toggle::after {
      content: ''; position: absolute; top: 3px; left: 3px;
      width: 22px; height: 22px; background: #fff;
      border-radius: 50%; transition: transform 0.25s cubic-bezier(.4,0,.2,1);
      box-shadow: 0 1px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
    }
    .toggle.on::after { transform: translateX(22px); }

    .xp-gain {
      font-size: 1.1em; font-weight: 800; color: var(--accent-purple);
      animation: xpPop 0.6s ease-out; text-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(168,85,247,0.35);
    }
    @keyframes xpPop { 0% { opacity: 0; transform: scale(0.5) translateY(10px); } 50% { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1.15) translateY(-5px); } 100% { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1) translateY(0); } }
    .motivational-nudge { font-size: 0.82em; opacity: 0.5; max-width: 280px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.6; }
    .milestone-unlock {
      display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 14px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255,215,0,0.08), rgba(255,107,107,0.04));
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,215,0,0.15); border-radius: var(--ui-radius);
      padding: 14px 20px; animation: milestoneSlide 0.5s ease-out;
    }
    @keyframes milestoneSlide { 0% { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px) scale(0.9); } 100% { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0) scale(1); } }
    .milestone-icon { font-size: 2.2em; }
    .milestone-label { font-size: 0.5em; opacity: 0.3; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 2px; }
    #milestone-name { font-size: 0.95em; font-weight: 800; color: var(--accent-gold); }

    #level-up-overlay {
      display: none; position: fixed; inset: 0;
      background: rgba(5,5,15,0.85); z-index: 250;
      flex-direction: column; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    }
    #level-up-overlay.show { display: flex; animation: fadeIn 0.3s ease-out; }
    .level-up-content { text-align: center; animation: levelUpBounce 0.6s ease-out; }
    @keyframes levelUpBounce { 0% { opacity: 0; transform: scale(0.3); } 50% { transform: scale(1.1); } 100% { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1); } }
    .level-up-icon { font-size: 3.5em; }
    .level-up-text { font-size: 2em; font-weight: 900; color: var(--accent-gold); margin: 8px 0; }
    .level-up-title { font-size: 1em; opacity: 0.5; }

    #stats-modal {
      display: none; position: fixed; inset: 0;
      background: rgba(5,5,15,0.92); z-index: 300;
      flex-direction: column; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      gap: 16px; backdrop-filter: blur(18px);
    }
    #stats-modal.show { display: flex; }
    .stats-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 8px; }
    .stat-card {
      background: var(--bg-card); border-radius: 12px; padding: 12px; text-align: center;
      border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
    }
    .stat-card .stat-value { font-size: 1.5em; font-weight: 900; }
    .stat-card .stat-label { font-size: 0.5em; opacity: 0.25; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1.5px; }
    .achievements-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 6px; }
    .achievement-row {
      display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; padding: 10px; border-radius: 10px; background: var(--bg-card);
    }
    .achievement-row.locked { opacity: 0.15; filter: grayscale(1); }
    .achievement-row .ach-icon { font-size: 1.5em; }
    .achievement-row .ach-name { font-size: 0.8em; font-weight: 700; }
    .achievement-row .ach-desc { font-size: 0.6em; opacity: 0.35; }
    #leaderboard-modal.show { display: flex; }
    .lb-row { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; padding: 10px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.03); font-size: 0.9em; }
    .lb-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
    .lb-name { flex: 1; font-weight: 600; }
    .lb-score { font-weight: 900; color: var(--accent-gold); font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums; }
    #tutorial-overlay.show { display: flex; animation: fadeIn 0.4s ease-out; }

    #combo-fire {
      position: absolute; bottom: -8px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%);
      font-size: 0; transition: font-size 0.3s ease-out;
      pointer-events: none; z-index: 10;
      filter: drop-shadow(0 0 8px rgba(255,100,0,0.5));
    }
    #combo-fire.active { font-size: 1.8em; }
    #combo-fire.mega { font-size: 2.5em; filter: drop-shadow(0 0 16px rgba(255,50,0,0.8)); }

    ::-webkit-scrollbar { width: 0; }
    @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
      *, *::before, *::after { animation-duration: 0.01ms !important; transition-duration: 0.01ms !important; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <canvas id="bg-canvas"></canvas>
  <canvas id="fx-canvas"></canvas>

  <div id="splash">
    <div class="splash-blocks" id="splash-blocks"></div>
    <div class="splash-logo-container">
      <div class="splash-icon">🧩</div>
      <div class="splash-title">BLOCK SMASH</div>
      <div class="splash-subtitle">PUZZLE</div>
    </div>
    <div class="splash-loader"><div class="splash-loader-fill"></div></div>
    <div class="splash-tap" id="splash-tap">TAP TO PLAY</div>
    <div class="splash-version">v3.0</div>
  </div>

  <div id="game-container">
    <div class="header">
      <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;">
        <div class="game-title">BLOCK SMASH</div>
      </div>
      <div class="header-right">
        <div class="score-section">
          <div class="score-box"><div class="label">Score</div><div class="value" id="score">0</div></div>
          <div class="score-box"><div class="label">Best</div><div class="value" id="best-score">0</div></div>
        </div>
        <button class="gear-btn" id="btn-settings" aria-label="Settings">⚙️</button>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div id="level-bar-container">
      <div class="level-info">
        <span id="level-badge">⭐ Lv.1</span>
        <span id="level-title" class="level-title-text">Rookie</span>
        <span id="streak-badge" class="streak-badge" style="display:none">🔥 0</span>
      </div>
      <div class="xp-bar-bg"><div class="xp-bar-fill" id="xp-bar-fill" style="width:0%"></div></div>
      <div class="xp-label"><span id="xp-text">0 / 200 XP</span></div>
    </div>
    <div id="daily-challenge" class="daily-challenge">
      <div class="daily-left">
        <span class="daily-icon" id="daily-icon">⚡</span>
        <div class="daily-info">
          <div class="daily-name" id="daily-name">Daily: Line Blitz</div>
          <div class="daily-desc" id="daily-desc">Clear 5 lines</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="daily-progress-ring" id="daily-ring"><span id="daily-progress-text">0/5</span></div>
    </div>
    <div id="board-container">
      <div class="board-toolbar">
        <button class="action-btn" id="btn-undo" style="opacity:0.3;pointer-events:none;" aria-label="Undo">↩ Undo</button>
        <span id="fill-percent" style="font-size:0.55em;opacity:0.15;font-weight:700;font-variant-numeric:tabular-nums;">0%</span>
        <button class="action-btn" id="btn-how-to-play" aria-label="How to play">❓ How</button>
      </div>
      <div id="board"></div>
      <div id="combo-fire"></div>
    </div>
    <div id="pieces-container"></div>
    <div class="ad-banner-slot" id="ad-banner" style="display:none;"></div>
  </div>

  <div id="drag-ghost"></div>

  <div id="game-over">
    <h2>GAME OVER</h2>
    <div class="final-score" id="final-score">0</div>
    <div class="new-record" id="new-record" style="display:none">🏆 NEW RECORD!</div>
    <div class="best-label">Best Score</div>
    <div class="best-score" id="final-best">0</div>
    <div id="xp-gain" class="xp-gain" style="display:none"><span id="xp-gain-text">+120 XP</span></div>
    <div id="motivational-nudge" class="motivational-nudge" style="display:none"></div>
    <div id="milestone-unlock" class="milestone-unlock" style="display:none">
      <div class="milestone-icon" id="milestone-icon">⭐</div>
      <div class="milestone-text">
        <div class="milestone-label">Achievement Unlocked!</div>
        <div id="milestone-name">First Clear</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="btn-row">
      <button class="btn btn-primary" id="btn-restart">▶ Play Again</button>
      <button class="btn btn-share" id="btn-share">Share 🔗</button>
    </div>
    <div class="btn-row" style="margin-top:4px;">
      <button class="btn btn-secondary" id="btn-leaderboard">🏅 Leaderboard</button>
      <button class="btn btn-secondary" id="btn-stats">📊 Stats</button>
    </div>
    <div class="btn-row" style="margin-top:4px;">
      <button class="btn btn-exit" id="btn-exit-game">✕ Exit Game</button>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div id="settings-modal">
    <div class="settings-panel">
      <h3>⚙️ Settings</h3>
      <div class="setting-row"><span>Sound Effects</span><div class="toggle on" id="toggle-sound"></div></div>
      <div class="setting-row"><span>Haptic Feedback</span><div class="toggle on" id="toggle-vibration"></div></div>
      <div class="setting-row"><span>Ambient Music</span><div class="toggle" id="toggle-music"></div></div>
      <div style="margin-top:18px;text-align:center;">
        <button class="btn btn-primary" id="btn-close-settings" style="padding:10px 28px;">Done</button>
      </div>
      <div style="margin-top:12px;text-align:center;">
        <button class="btn btn-exit" id="btn-exit-settings" style="padding:8px 24px;font-size:0.85em;">✕ Exit Game</button>
      </div>
      <div style="margin-top:18px;text-align:center;opacity:0.15;font-size:0.6em;">
        <a href="/privacy" style="color:#fff;">Privacy Policy</a> · v3.0
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div id="stats-modal">
    <div class="settings-panel" style="max-width:380px;max-height:80vh;overflow-y:auto;">
      <h3>📊 Your Stats</h3>
      <div class="stats-grid" id="stats-grid"></div>
      <h3 style="margin-top:16px;">🏆 Achievements</h3>
      <div id="achievements-list" class="achievements-list"></div>
      <div style="margin-top:16px;text-align:center;">
        <button class="btn btn-primary" id="btn-close-stats" style="padding:10px 28px;">Done</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div id="level-up-overlay">
    <div class="level-up-content">
      <div class="level-up-icon">🎉</div>
      <div class="level-up-text" id="level-up-text">LEVEL 2!</div>
      <div class="level-up-title" id="level-up-title">Beginner</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div id="leaderboard-modal" style="display:none;position:fixed;inset:0;background:rgba(5,5,15,0.92);z-index:300;align-items:center;justify-content:center;backdrop-filter:blur(18px);">
    <div class="settings-panel" style="max-width:380px;max-height:80vh;overflow-y:auto;">
      <h3>🏅 Leaderboard</h3>
      <div id="leaderboard-list" style="margin:12px 0;"></div>
      <div style="text-align:center;">
        <button class="btn btn-primary" id="btn-close-leaderboard" style="padding:10px 28px;">Done</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div id="tutorial-overlay" style="display:none;position:fixed;inset:0;background:rgba(5,5,15,0.94);z-index:350;align-items:center;justify-content:center;backdrop-filter:blur(18px);">
    <div class="settings-panel" style="max-width:360px;text-align:center;">
      <h3 style="margin-bottom:14px;">🧩 How to Play</h3>
      <div style="text-align:left;font-size:0.88em;line-height:2;opacity:0.85;">
        <div>👆 <strong>Drag & drop</strong> blocks onto the board</div>
        <div>📏 <strong>Fill complete rows or columns</strong> to clear them</div>
        <div>🔥 <strong>Chain clears</strong> for combo multipliers!</div>
        <div>✨ <strong>Clear entire board</strong> for Perfect Clear bonus!</div>
        <div>↩ <strong>Undo</strong> your last move</div>
        <div>🎯 <strong>Daily challenges</strong> give bonus XP</div>
        <div>💀 <strong>Game ends</strong> when no pieces fit</div>
      </div>
      <div style="margin-top:8px;padding:12px;background:rgba(255,215,0,0.05);border-radius:12px;font-size:0.78em;opacity:0.45;">
        💡 <strong>Pro tip:</strong> Keep the center clear and build from edges!
      </div>
      <div style="margin-top:18px;">
        <button class="btn btn-primary" id="btn-tutorial-close" style="padding:14px 44px;font-size:1.1em;">Let's Play 🎮</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <script src="/game.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
